Post-Match Reflections: Bangladesh knocked out of semi-finals race in CWC 2023
Miscellaneous Highlights: Netherlands ended Bangladesh's hopes of qualifying for the semi-finals in the ongoing ICC Men's Cricket World Cup 2023 by handing them an 87-run defeat at the Eden Gardens in Kolkata.
With this win, Netherlands moved up to the eighth spot in the World Cup 2023 points table, sending defending champions England to the bottom.
